            .col-sm-6.col-12.info_right
                .card.card_info_right
                    .card-body
                        h2.card-title.text-center The Willwriting Partnership
                        h4.card-title.text-center More than just a will-writing service
                        p.card-text
                            | The Willwriting Partnership has been established since 1999. Featured in the Rochdale Observer, on Salford City Radio, Rossendale Radio and in other media in our area, we are still here and still going strong. Laws relating to your estate can change and we will endeavour to get in touch whenever there is something you can do to take advantage of a change. We will be available if you need us in the future and are just at the end of the phone for any advice relating to your Will, your estate or the protection of your assets.
                        .text-center
                            a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href="{{ 'history'|page }} ") Discover More
    .container
        h3 What we do...
        p.lead
            i.fa.fa-info-circle.fa-2x(aria-hidden='true')
            |    We help honest, hard-working people to make sure their assets go to the people they want to inherit.
        p  We make sure your cheating ex-husband doesn’t inherit your money!
        p  We make sure you don’t leave a mess when you die.
        p
            | We protect your assets from the con-men, identity thieves and criminals that target the elderly.
        p
            | We help you as a concerned parent to appoint guardians in case you pass away whilst your children are young.
        p
            | We put working-class and middle-class families on a level playing field with the rich and powerful that use the legal means to keep money in the bloodline.
