                .carousel-item.active
                    img.mx-auto.d-block.img-fluid(src="img/tes339.jpg", alt='First slide')
                    .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block
                        h3 Colin, Littleborough
                        p
                            i.fa.fa-quote-left(aria-hidden='true')
                            |  Your approach to taking care of the will writing and telling us just what was necessary was a great lesson in itself.
                            i.fa.fa-quote-right(aria-hidden='true')
