                            i.fa.fa-quote-left(aria-hidden='true')
                            |  The service was thorough, polite, caring and above all most professional. We were so impressed, nothing was too much trouble. You made what can be a rather sombre time an ease to deal with.
                            i.fa.fa-quote-right(aria-hidden='true')
                .carousel-item
                    img.mx-auto.d-block.img-fluid(src="img/tes658.jpg", alt='Third slide')
                    .carousel-caption.d-none.d-md-block
                        h3 Andrea, Rochdale
                        p
                            i.fa.fa-quote-left(aria-hidden='true')
                            |  he service was very well structured and easy to understand. I found the service to be very professional, well organised and yet at the same time also very personal to my needs, and very relaxed.
                            i.fa.fa-quote-right(aria-hidden='true')
